    "Authoritative gate is the on-chain is_supported_mint function, a CLOSED ALLOWLIST. Token-2022 mints pass only if EVERY extension is one of {TransferFeeConfig, MetadataPointer, TokenMetadata, InterestBearingConfig, ScaledUiAmount}; anything else reverts.",
